As an Administrator, I would like to specify the "Created After" attribute to be a rolling period. ie: Within the last 30 days

For example, I expected to be able to input "30d" in the field and have it show me the tasks that have been created within the last 30 days. I intend to use this in connection with "Completed" tasks, such that I can have an ongoing list of tasks that have been completed, and that have been created within the last 30 days.

Use Case: In our team meetings we'd like to review the tasks that have been completed and that have been created within the last 30 days, or whatever period we designate (rather than a fixed date in the format of dd-mm-yyy)

